Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.49,0:01:43.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…选哪个好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.07,0:01:45.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说你是要给谁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.02,0:01:47.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和朋友们一起吃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.91,0:01:50.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…我就猜是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.30,0:01:54.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子之间互相交换巧克力也很有趣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.59,0:01:59.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿兹特克文明  咖啡因  可可
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.69,0:02:07.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:09.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？怎么了  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.29,0:02:12.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也教教我怎么做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.77,0:02:15.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好啊  夏奈你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.33,0:02:21.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我就算了  情人节跟我没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.43,0:02:25.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你反正会用天生的贪婪的性格
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.55,0:02:28.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那些受欢迎的男生手里抢巧克力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.59,0:02:30.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…哦——
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.50,0:02:31.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.67,0:02:32.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.19,0:02:37.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊！可以吃个够啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:41.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…这可不是在给你提什么好建议
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.44,0:02:45.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机会难得  夏奈也一起做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.67,0:02:48.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉～我就算了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.24,0:02:52.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送礼不如收礼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.48,0:02:55.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行哦  这可是女孩子的庆典呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:02:57.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.27,0:02:58.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.87,0:03:01.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以夏奈也要一起做  好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.88,0:03:05.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庆典…节日  节日！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.34,0:03:11.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要反击了！睡衣派对上春香的招待实在太抢眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.39,0:03:15.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会又想什么歪点子吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:18.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  把大家都叫来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.76,0:03:20.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召开情人节庆典！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.76,0:03:22.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.89,0:03:27.89,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}第7碗  越嚼越甜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.61,0:03:34.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  都准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.22,0:03:36.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.01,0:03:41.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我要穿成这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:43.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:46.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是阿珍  是女孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.31,0:03:48.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情人节是女孩子的庆典
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.52,0:03:50.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不参加怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.90,0:03:52.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…可是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.69,0:03:55.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？你想说自己不是女的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.64,0:03:57.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱们的友情还真是短暂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.45,0:04:02.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.13,0:04:03.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.23,0:04:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是…以后不准出入这里了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:18.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  我做就是了  我会努力帮忙的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.63,0:04:29.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐  我能帮什么忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.01,0:04:31.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想做什么样的巧克力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.81,0:04:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…啊  可爱点的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.86,0:04:37.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把巧克力分成小块
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:43.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我会把它切得更碎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.21,0:04:44.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.31,0:04:50.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  为什么我要来这儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:52.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是节日嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:54.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.18,0:04:57.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不打算送给谁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.53,0:04:58.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.54,0:05:00.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会送啦  那种东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.73,0:05:02.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有哥哥吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.96,0:05:05.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给哥哥？怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.32,0:05:08.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  真是个孤僻的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.02,0:05:11.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我很孤僻吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.51,0:05:16.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:20.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等你很久了  快点儿进来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.64,0:05:21.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.42,0:05:23.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.32,0:05:25.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真热闹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.19,0:05:34.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…很孤僻吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:40.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还顺利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.55,0:05:42.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？还行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.33,0:05:45.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋你要送给谁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:49.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内田要把巧克力送给谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.63,0:05:52.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  完全没想过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.75,0:05:54.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个没计划的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.52,0:06:02.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野  你要把巧克力送给谁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.10,0:06:05.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给爸爸  昨天做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.63,0:06:08.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  一群无聊的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.98,0:06:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说夏奈你要送谁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:13.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只负责收
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.70,0:06:24.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊  要你们两个来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.07,0:06:26.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事儿啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.91,0:06:29.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊  反正有空嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.18,0:06:31.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.60,0:06:33.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真碍事  给我出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.79,0:06:34.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.92,0:06:36.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小气小气小气！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:39.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈还是一样那么有活力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.88,0:06:40.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.56,0:06:43.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍要把巧克力送给谁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.03,0:06:44.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.18,0:06:49.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春…春香姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.36,0:06:50.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.09,0:06:52.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.05,0:06:54.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说不准
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.41,0:06:56.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.13,0:06:57.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.21,0:07:01.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过机会难得  送给男孩子怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.66,0:07:02.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.95,0:07:04.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有想送的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.41,0:07:07.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有想送的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.91,0:07:10.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔  原来有那样的对象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.10,0:07:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.84,0:07:18.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿…阿真同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.74,0:07:19.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦——
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:23.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪  你见过阿真？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.42,0:07:26.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那个…应该吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.73,0:07:29.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就直说了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.62,0:07:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是放弃他吧  他就是个智障儿童
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.86,0:07:34.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.56,0:07:39.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力真是好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.14,0:07:42.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗  这不是备用的巧克力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.28,0:07:44.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.57,0:07:49.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.45,0:07:50.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.22,0:07:53.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果真是个孤僻的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.26,0:07:55.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？哲学性的问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:07:58.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.84,0:08:13.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.54,0:08:15.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题  没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.24,0:08:24.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.66,0:08:26.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  做得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.62,0:08:29.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不是我动手  可还是会紧张呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.29,0:08:31.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  这才刚开始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.18,0:08:38.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪儿啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.57,0:08:39.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.46,0:08:45.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪  怎么就化不开呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.99,0:09:00.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微火…超微火
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.76,0:09:03.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错啊  融化的巧克力也够美味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.34,0:09:05.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！干什么呢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.18,0:09:17.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.06,0:09:19.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试吃一下就光光了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.26,0:09:21.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我滚！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.20,0:09:27.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  做得不错  就那样继续拌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.00,0:09:31.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊  阿珍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.24,0:09:34.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么擅长家事  你随时都可以嫁人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.38,0:09:38.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫁人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.70,0:09:40.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  什么焦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.21,0:09:43.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.89,0:09:45.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了来了  我这就来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.45,0:09:49.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.41,0:09:58.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马  冬马  快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.43,0:10:01.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.97,0:10:03.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力貌似不够了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.07,0:10:04.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.14,0:10:07.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去买回来  马上去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.60,0:10:08.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.58,0:10:09.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是吃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.10,0:10:10.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.60,0:10:14.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不赶紧去买  你这蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:15.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.40,0:10:23.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.02,0:10:24.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.84,0:10:28.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈不也吃巧克力了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.12,0:10:30.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！冬马
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.75,0:10:32.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  藤冈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.52,0:10:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  买完东西回家？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:39.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…夏奈叫我去买巧克力啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.86,0:10:42.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？南让你买  为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.99,0:10:46.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那个  因为让我帮她做啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.59,0:10:51.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要男生帮忙吗  那我也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.27,0:10:52.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.84,0:10:53.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.55,0:10:57.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说…你看…可能是准备送给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.36,0:11:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定不愿意被本人看到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.00,0:11:05.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…走了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.15,0:11:11.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南给我…巧克力…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.32,0:11:17.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我买回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.45,0:11:19.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢死了  冬马
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.42,0:11:22.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你  让我遭罪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.43,0:11:24.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.13,0:11:29.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等稍微凝固一下  就可以装饰了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.78,0:11:43.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经凝固了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.41,0:11:44.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还早啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.75,0:11:46.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就说还早呢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:50.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之告一段落了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.42,0:11:51.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来喝茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.90,0:11:52.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:07.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.01,0:12:11.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好像买完东西就回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.44,0:12:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是累了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.45,0:12:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她明明什么都没干
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.14,0:12:18.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍也回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.63,0:12:20.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没耐性的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.44,0:12:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我收到了阿珍的巧克力  真幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.57,0:12:28.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到头来还是没给阿真  没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.02,0:12:30.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.54,0:12:32.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概明白他是白痴了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:39.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  给我巧克力吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.67,0:12:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  剩下那些你随便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.75,0:12:48.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要再来一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:51.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀  抱歉  没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:53.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.76,0:12:56.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  千秋要送给谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.10,0:13:05.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  就是那家伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.91,0:13:07.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔壁的冬木
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.38,0:13:08.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.27,0:13:08.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.16,0:13:10.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉～这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.24,0:13:13.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.39,0:13:14.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.72,0:13:16.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别害羞  别害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.61,0:13:19.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那儿胡说八道什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.68,0:13:23.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  不管送谁  对方能高兴就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.77,0:13:26.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  年轻真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:46.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.48,0:13:47.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜…！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:55.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  好吃吧  这可是为你特制的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.87,0:13:59.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼泪都流出来啦  开心就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.47,0:14:09.90,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(蠢货)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.14,0:14:14.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.27,0:14:16.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  千秋  帮帮忙啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.19,0:14:19.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  现在别烦我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.68,0:14:22.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.65,0:14:24.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦  我来帮你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.92,0:14:35.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…春香姐姐  抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.12,0:14:37.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那样盯着我看…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.58,0:14:40.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对不起  千秋  你慢慢做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.63,0:14:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:44.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得很漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.63,0:14:45.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.66,0:14:47.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:51.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有男生可以送就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.05,0:14:53.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明只是个小学生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.16,0:14:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就开始搞这些你情我爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:58.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光吃不做的家伙没资格这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.75,0:15:02.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要接受对方  巧克力就毫无价值
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.69,0:15:05.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也有人会因为这无价值的东西而感到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.74,0:15:09.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情人节真是无可挑剔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.26,0:15:17.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  藤冈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.62,0:15:18.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.96,0:15:27.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:30.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一份人情巧克力也不能收
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:33.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要全都还回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.82,0:15:36.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…是谁送的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.00,0:15:37.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤冈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.55,0:15:42.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早…早啊  南同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.74,0:15:45.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤冈  你是不是收了很多巧克力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.82,0:15:47.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个也没有收到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.04,0:15:48.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.35,0:15:55.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.59,0:15:59.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找个机会把巧克力送给藤冈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:01.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能收下就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.16,0:16:07.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.04,0:16:10.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防止别人送巧克力给藤冈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.20,0:16:16.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真碍事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.20,0:16:20.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点让开啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.41,0:16:24.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要站那儿多久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.18,0:16:28.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有要送的迹象呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:35.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小仓鼠  你看～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:37.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来很好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.84,0:16:42.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小仓鼠也想要巧克力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.63,0:16:44.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.16,0:16:49.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！我的巧克力…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.17,0:16:51.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别随便喂它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.31,0:16:57.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送给你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.87,0:16:59.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马  收下巧克力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.89,0:17:00.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？我？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.98,0:17:04.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因为冬马比男生还要帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.40,0:17:05.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就算了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.07,0:17:08.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  也给我们一些啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.74,0:17:09.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  接着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.19,0:17:13.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.59,0:17:17.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这回你可是名副其实的男生了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.31,0:17:31.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  让我吃块巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.38,0:17:35.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然春香做什么都好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:44.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊  保坂学长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.14,0:17:50.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想什么时候把这个送给她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.35,0:17:51.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.49,0:17:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用了最高级的比利时巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.47,0:18:02.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倾尽全力所做的蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.23,0:18:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.55,0:18:08.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是南春香白色情人节的回礼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.85,0:18:10.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回礼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:15.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想春香并没有给保坂学长巧克力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.49,0:18:16.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.44,0:18:19.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情人节只有今天而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.14,0:18:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有计划随便行动的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.49,0:18:27.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.61,0:18:29.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.24,0:18:32.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:36.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这学校谁最受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.06,0:18:37.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.19,0:18:41.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石川学长吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:43.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.65,0:18:44.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.07,0:18:48.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那家伙应该还剩很多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.33,0:18:52.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.67,0:18:54.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉…已经不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.88,0:18:55.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.93,0:19:03.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.65,0:19:07.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道藤冈去哪儿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.14,0:19:10.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他猛地冲出去  四处还巧克力去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.91,0:19:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.87,0:19:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是不是讨厌吃巧克力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:16.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.40,0:19:24.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把下一节课要用的资料拿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.39,0:19:28.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  不是一个班的还要麻烦你  真是谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.72,0:19:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  顺便而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.96,0:19:32.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢啦  这个巧克力拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.07,0:19:34.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉…我就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.22,0:19:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的也给你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.24,0:19:36.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.37,0:19:38.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收下吧  给
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.16,0:19:42.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…好  真是谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.77,0:19:45.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  你不给他巧克力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.48,0:19:46.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:47.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.64,0:19:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不明摆着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.12,0:20:02.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到的全都还回去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.61,0:20:05.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可最后也没收到南同学的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.05,0:20:07.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤冈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.40,0:20:09.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.73,0:20:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  一脸两手空空的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.56,0:20:24.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这儿有很多哦  分一点儿给不受欢迎的你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.43,0:20:27.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.80,0:20:30.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.82,0:20:42.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  我给你们两个的情人节礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.14,0:20:45.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.58,0:20:49.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～谢谢你  春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.32,0:20:54.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  千秋你到底送给谁了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.48,0:21:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请收下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.99,0:21:02.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？给我？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.49,0:21:07.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.90,0:21:09.41,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(春香姐姐  谢谢你)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.76,0:21:11.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.56,0:21:16.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  希望有一天你不是给我而是给真正喜欢的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:20.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…对春香姐姐是一心一意的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.14,0:21:22.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  我的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.58,0:21:39.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉简直太浪费了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.22,0:21:44.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  那就由我来…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.69,0:21:47.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.50,0:21:49.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊  你这家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.72,0:21:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃腻这又黑又甜的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.75,0:21:58.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我舔盐去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.37,0:22:00.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别…别这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.77,0:22:20.77,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の奥集めた　今日の光を持って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.77,0:22:20.77,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}怀揣着内心深处收集好了的今天的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.42,0:22:29.56,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}飛び込んだ未知の先　何が待ってるのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.42,0:22:29.56,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}跃入未知的前方　那里有什么正等待着我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.85,0:22:38.90,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}未来への共鳴　想い出に重ねれば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.85,0:22:38.90,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}若是与未来共鸣　不断忆起今天的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.10,0:22:47.94,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}勇気になる　強さになる　一人じゃないから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.10,0:22:47.94,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就会生出勇气　就能变得坚强　也就不再是独自一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.13,0:22:50.25,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（聴かせて）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.13,0:22:50.25,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（让你倾听）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.34,0:22:58.87,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明日もきっと会えるね　本当の笑顔で行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.34,0:22:58.87,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明天也一定会与你相遇　我会带着真诚的笑容前去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.06,0:23:07.75,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夢見る夜明けを　一緒に迎えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.06,0:23:07.75,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}好想和你一起迎接梦想中的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.92,0:23:16.93,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}無限の時間よりも　瞬間を駆け抜けよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.92,0:23:16.93,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}与其坐拥这无限的时刻　倒不如追赶那绚烂的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.18,0:23:28.13,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}その夢の声いつか聴かせてね　信じてく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.18,0:23:28.13,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}相信我　总有一天会让你倾听那梦中的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.59,0:23:34.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道笊篱荞麦和蒸笼荞麦的区别吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.73,0:23:36.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说是过去用的蘸汁不同
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.05,0:23:38.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笊篱荞麦用的首锅汤汁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.38,0:23:40.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒸笼荞麦则用再煎熬的汤汁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.41,0:23:43.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就只知道加紫菜的是笊篱荞麦了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.42,0:23:46.22,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\an8\fad(370,0)}第8碗  「游泳池是同父异母的姐妹」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.67,0:23:45.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～突然想吃荞麦面了
